message:
East Idaho Newsmakers: Child sex trafficking and exploitation in eastern Idaho.
Eaton and Smith talk about what’s being done to stop the problem, what parents need to know and how common sex trafficking and child exploitation is in east Idaho.

data.description: In this edition of East Idaho Newsmakers, Nate Eaton speaks with the Matt Smith, the executive director of Operation Shield. Operation Shield is a local non-profit organization dedicated to…
